{
  "texts": [
    "We suspect that the model performance has saturated due to the presence of SQuAD in the task-specialized training dataset.",
    "To further improve on extractive question answering, we could benefit from having access to a few examples from the target dataset.",
    "Finally, we almost always improve performance on Vitamin C and PubMedQA datasets highlighting the importance of training on more task samples (see Section 6.2).",
    "Here we study the effect of the size of the training dataset.",
    "In particular, we study how Mistral-7B performance varies when trained on different quantities of synthetic instruction tuning data for PubMedQA and Vitamin C. Figure 3 shows that training on more steps typically improves perfor- mance."
  ]
}